data.description: This rambler is light and bright with large entertainment-sized Family Room, and vaulted ceilings. The custom hexagon layout gives the home unique angles with high Ceilings! Amenities include a Formal Dining Area, extra large Kitchen With Pantry, and lovely tiled entry. There is an office or spare room, use your imagination. Sold as is. Buyer to verify all information.
